---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    background: "#ffffff"
    fontFamily: "Arial"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant E2E as Karmadactl E2E
    participant Pod as Test Pod<br/>(nginx + busybox)
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet / Runtime
    participant Metrics as metrics.k8s.io
    participant CLI as karmadactl top

    E2E->>Pod: Create the same Pod on each member
    Pod-->>E2E: Observe Pod phase Running

    loop One readiness check per member
        E2E->>Metrics: GET PodMetrics
        Metrics-->>E2E: Found at this instant
    end
    Note over E2E,Metrics: A successful one-shot read does not keep later metrics available.

    E2E->>CLI: Query member1, then member2
    CLI->>Metrics: GET PodMetrics
    Metrics-->>CLI: Found

    Pod-xKubelet: busybox exits immediately (03:45:32.867Z)
    Kubelet-xMetrics: Collection fails: ttrpc closed (03:45:33.230Z)
    Kubelet-->>Pod: Enter CrashLoopBackOff (03:45:33.715Z)

    E2E->>CLI: Query member3
    CLI->>Metrics: GET PodMetrics
    Metrics-xCLI: PodMetrics NotFound (03:45:36.237Z)
    CLI-xE2E: Return non-zero and trigger fail-fast interruption

    Note over E2E,Metrics: E4 target: keep the fixture stable from readiness through final consumption.
